sentence: In trading on Monday, the Consumer Staples Select Sector SPDR Fund ETF ( XLP ) is outperforming other ETFs, up about 0.5% on the day.
Components of that ETF showing particular strength include shares of Whole Foods Market ( WFM ), up about 1.3% and shares of Procter & Gamble ( PG ), up about 1.2% on the day.
And underperforming other ETFs today is the iShares Latin America 40 ETF ( ILF ), down about 4.1% in Monday afternoon trading.
Among components of that ETF with the weakest showing on Monday were shares of Petroleo Brasileiro (PBR.A), lower by about 16.2%, and shares of CEMIG ( CIG ), lower by about 12% on the day.
